markets.title: Will Donda by Kanye West win Album of the Year at the Grammys by February 7?
markets.subtitle: Donda, Kanye West
markets.rules_primary: If Donda by Kanye West has won Album of the Year at the 64th Annual Grammy Awards, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
This Contract will close and expire the sooner of one day following the Grammys posting the winners on their website and February 07, 2022.
 
Important clarification for those who have traded in Kalshi's markets on the Grammys as of 1/5/22: news sources reported today that the Grammys ceremony, originally scheduled for January 31, 2022, has been delayed indefinitely. It's important for us to make sure that we adhere to the rules established by our contracts. As noted in the Rulebook, the contracts resolve based on who the winner is as measured at the Expiration Time on the Expiration Date. If no winners are announced by the Source Agency (the website of the Grammys) by the latest possible Expiration Date (February 7th, 2022) at the Expiration Time (10:00 AM) then all markets will resolve to No.
